=== 9.5 The Code: Transformer Block in Python

Layer normalization operates on a single vector: compute its mean and standard deviation, then shift each entry to mean 0, variance 1.
Learned parameters stem:[\gamma] and stem:[\beta] then rescale and shift the normalized result.

[source,python]
----
include::../../../src/python/microgpt.py[tag=layer_norm]
----

`layer-norm-matrix` applies `layer-norm-vec` independently to each row of a stem:[[T \times d\]] matrix.

[source,python]
----
include::../../../src/python/microgpt.py[tag=transformer_block]
----

`transformer-block-forward` is the Pre-LN residual block.

[source,python]
